<section xmlns:ns0="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
  <num>21-585</num>
  <heading>Confinement in jail prohibited.</heading>
  <text>A person apprehended, detained, or hospitalized under any provision of this chapter may not be confined in jail or in a penal or correctional institution.</text>
